high_descs: Walk across the room towards the sink, then hang a left and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter.
Walk over to the microwave that is on the counter behind you.
Put the tomato in the microwave and microwave it for a couple seconds, then take it out.
Turn left to face the counter.
Put the heated tomato on the front edge of the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the counter.

Place the tomato in the microwave, then take it out.
Place the tomato on the counter.
